### Test Rate Limiting cho các routes khác nhau

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 1: Lấy JWT Token trước
### ========================================

### 1.1. Generate Token (Rate limit: 10/phút)
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json
ClientId: test-client-1

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

