### 3.1. Pricing GET - Request 1 (should work)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-pricing

### 3.2. Pricing GET - Request 2 (should work)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-pricing

### 3.3. Pricing GET - Request 3 (should work)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-pricing

### 3.4. Pricing GET - Request 4 (should work)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-pricing

### 3.5. Pricing GET - Request 5 (should work)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-pricing

### 3.6. Pricing GET - Request 6 (should be rate limited - 429)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-pricing

