### ========================================
### BƯỚC 6: Test Rate Limiting cho POST/PUT/DELETE (limits khác nhau)
### ========================================

### 6.1. POST Pricing (20/phút)
POST http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "basePrice": 1000,
  "quantity": 5,
  "taxRate": 0.1
}

### 6.2. PUT Pricing (15/phút)
PUT http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-put
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPrice": 1500,
  "newPrice": 1800
}

### 6.3. DELETE Pricing (5/phút - strict limit)
DELETE http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
ClientId: test-client-delete

### ========================================
### EXPECTED RESULTS
### ========================================
### - Auth routes: 10 requests/phút
### - Pricing GET: 5 requests/giây
### - Pricing GET by ID: 3 requests/giây  
### - Policy GET: 2 requests/giây
### - Pricing POST: 20 requests/phút
### - Pricing PUT: 15 requests/phút
### - Pricing DELETE: 5 requests/phút
### - Rate limit exceeded: 429 status với message custom